Package javachr.constraints

Class ConstraintStore

java.lang.Object
javachr.constraints.ConstraintStore
public class ConstraintStore
extends java.lang.Object
Holds a set of constraints. Constraints can be added with add(Constraint) method and as constructor parameter.

    • getAll

      public java.util.List<Constraint<?>> getAll()
      Returns the list that stores all the Constraints. Attention: It's the same list as used for storage. Manipulation of the list leads to manipulation of the ConstraintStore.
      Returns:
      A list with all Constraints the ConstraintStore holds.
